{
  "stem": "1929.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think he assisted us a lot in-- in being-- in saving us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's not his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't find his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's some place on the record.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I can't-- I couldn't find his name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think maybe Bernstein or something like that, but I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I've never seen any part of his family, any reference to his part of the family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hassim something.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hassim Kovar.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some name like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think there were more-- yeah, I think so.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hassim something.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she got married and she had her own apartment, a very nice apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was the sister that I remember taking care of me more than, than my mother, because she was-- I remember her as being very warm, very loving, very caring towards me.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I spent a lot of time in her apartment because I was, by far, the youngest one of the family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was kind of a devil, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was very hard to control.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody could really control me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't even invite me to her-- well, they did invite me to her wedding, but apparently, what happened was that they didn't want me at the wedding because they were afraid that I would make a commotion or something.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That shows you how behaved I was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they send me to my aunt, Rachel, who lived about-- oh, I don't know, maybe about a mile away or something like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she got so mad at the fact that I was not at my sister's wedding that I remember my, my cousin, my young cousin, took me on his bicycle and he wheeled me to-- to the-- The wedding took place in the house, in our apartment.",
      "word_count": 47
    }
  ],
